57 ** Device type UARTLP changed to UART0.

64 ** - rev. 1.5 (2013-04-05)
65 ** Changed start of doxygen comment.
66 ** - rev. 1.6 (2013-04-11)
67 ** SystemInit methods updated with predefined initialization sequence.
68 ** - rev. 1.7 (2014-02-10)
69 ** Access restriction of some registers fixed.
70 ** Startup file for gcc has been updated according to CMSIS 3.2.
71 ** The declaration of clock configurations has been moved to separate header file system_MKL05Z4.h
72 ** - rev. 2.0 (2014-08-22)
73 ** Register accessor macros added to the memory map.
74 ** Symbols for Processor Expert memory map compatibility added to the memory map.
75 ** Module access macro module_BASES replaced by module_BASE_PTRS.
76 ** System initialization and startup updated.
77 ** - rev. 2.1 (2014-08-28)
78 ** Update of startup files - possibility to override DefaultISR added.
79 ** - rev. 2.2 (2014-10-14)
80 ** Interrupt INT_LPTimer renamed to INT_LPTMR0.
81 ** - rev. 2.3 (2015-02-19)
82 ** Renamed interrupt vector LLW to LLWU.
83 **

905 /* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
906  -- DMA Peripheral Access Layer
907  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
908 
915 typedef struct {
916  uint8_t RESERVED_0[256];
917  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
918  __IO uint32_t SAR;
919  __IO uint32_t DAR;
920  union { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
921  __IO uint32_t DSR_BCR;
922  struct { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
923  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
924  __IO uint8_t DSR;
925  } DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT;
926  };
927  __IO uint32_t DCR;
928  } DMA[4];
929 } DMA_Type, *DMA_MemMapPtr;
